{"tid":11510,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"養唔養好 好迷茫....","createTime":"2016-11-29T10:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T11:11:05.000Z","uid":40327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b9249c3096ba58433ce3615c0630a1e40fbd47","tid":11510,"uid":40327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的 本人好鐘意狗<br />\n但個屋苑寫到明係唔比養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我成日搭lift都會見到有人用狗袋袋住隻狗出街<br />\n我問過我屋企人 佢地都唔反對我養 <br />\n我有諗過領養 但個地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但如果有人投訴 隻狗點算  我又冇理由趕走隻狗 <br />\n但我又真係好想養 點算....<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4674fbfa75a2031b965d8b8f011477babb280dbd","tid":11510,"uid":22281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:14:08.000Z","msg":"好似有得同屋苑申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a752b453decfc9cefa33a2c7ab96050fd6eae54f","tid":11510,"uid":8534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"唔好養！"},{"pid":"92faa5d5998ba8999556567ef4a23164dc89a421","tid":11510,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5afc721e46cef147bcca91aeef4ff172d2881100","tid":11510,"uid":21173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"考慮下幾個問題<br />\n去外遊 邊個幫你睇狗<br />\n狗糧錢 睇你個樣都係學生啦 你每個月比唔比到<br />\n時間 夠唔夠黎陪佢  放狗？<br />\n清理屎尿怕唔怕噁心<br />\n最後 錢<br />\n早幾日隻狗斷左骨要做手術<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/191049_9dad2401b4f0c61903652c6aea9fe103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F191049_9dad2401b4f0c61903652c6aea9fe103.jpg&h=bcc659b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n覺得接受到就養"}]}